description: Stir-fried ramen noodles with chicken mince and pak choy, and topped with crunchy cashews, make a delicious dinner that can be on the table in 20 minutes.
name: Simple Chicken & Corn Stir-Fried Noodles Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 175 g chicken & cashew nut meal base

recipeInstructions.text: Add noodles, meal base and corn, then cook for 2 minutes, stirring, or until heated through. Divide noodle mixture among bowls. Serve topped with cashews.
